化学" target="_blank">化学</a>工程PhD学位项目，MS极少情况下招生，被录取新生不要求硕士学位，可获得全额<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，包括全部学费和相当可观的生活费用。</p><p>该项目设有以下研究领域：</p><ul>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/生物工程" target="_blank">生物工程</a>（Bioengineering）</li>	<li>生物燃料和可持续能源（Biofuels and Sustainable Energy）</li>	<li>流体力学和迁移现象（Fluid Mechanics and Transport Phenomena）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/材料科学与工程" target="_blank">材料科学与工程</a>（Materials Science and Engineering）</li>	<li>分子和多尺度建模与仿真（Molecular and Multi-scale Modeling &amp; Simulation）*(3)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRYDLZv0OWY0CCCCCesTUajvqxFW2c2czrR1bfGvzri-U0bEL_4KXQVKxn0Gr74OxQ2mqBV3pW6jXD89-DTAX38E-PJWsAbQMAIWUWGSs2xR7lIQMAH6eCmWsAO5six_9AHS8DxvvqeO2NmhbqJU3Tru2Q_P" target="_blank">Tuition &amp; Aid</a>&nbsp;Chemical Engineering Department UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTIDw-IwEQPbNNNNNGbke_8ACbPs261j1jCY84LPeMd6FV48ugq80pixuo9sRiXy6RMkZieYalAw6iqItYnPcRCWn3FAlZH1CLXpCkh4PBio2IHLa8GPer" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4AscwDkbcX2zjv9Xg6FhUQX9vjtF0CxTjCWS9i37-BpxV8V3hhLKpn8Z_xWmmS-fSUnUenROKY_UJ_Z" target="_blank">Graduate Students</a> Chemical Engineering Department UMass Amherst</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>土木工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:76px">			<p>50(40)</p>			</td>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>$4,968.50</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>1月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:95px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:76px">			<p>80</p>			</td>			<td style="width:85px">			<p><a 