f Science in Geography，接受秋季学期入学申请，截止日期为2月1日。*(5)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>该项目设有以下研究领域：</p><ul>	<li>环境地质学/全球变化（Environmental Geology/Global Change）</li>	<li>固态地质学（Solid Earth Geology）</li>	<li>地理（Geography）*(9)</li></ul><p>地球科学系向其研究生提供<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/Merit-based" target="_blank">Merit-based</a><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，形式主要有<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>或<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>奖学金。*(10)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>地球科学系宣传册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7m1ZLDXYcxHCAAA6jjzigqwZfquH1nxMFMfsDNEQ1CodD9SQ1PoOFKLlprv5DF-BEujijMZimAlpjxLyXelpIN-WEM6iZvjpXd-pIxjiDCj52N-ybV" target="_blank">Geosciences at a Glance</a> (PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDOktZGde7_nnnnns_bVPdwKsXYhni5i5Xe-RKu8sh2zF730CH3REUpOXS0Ldi4KR2OKtmuGmm1jhEAHI67a-lh1r0l0EflsjAK7dYmVj7iZAMYSK0zsJ" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKNKLLRfqSulffffffH4_e7oIzZMx0qyqyWsZY1bfGvzriHZHUvZ3JhlKZ8kEIL6PjT_E8btU9QXmrdE7a2nHw58W" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIeztgrkQ2RhN4PqqqldddM4iCp0JFlDU9U9-_usjAT9NXx0UAThNCXDEBzsUypDECf0qB-9qXfsjC1" target="_blank">CNS Departments</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEb1LSONzWOd------It3ipJ5W8rS8K1K1Zpy-m95SDuWX2w2IBwYp5Lkjgur3l72A1KW8OKLbsfOhsr" target="_blank">Graduate Programs and Application Deadlines</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVdNkGpktrcOiiiiiirJkgafCTNRbzbzqypF8hvz8EBfbHvF8gERb0qd