理科或工程某领域的知识。申请者最好是毕业于本科数学专业，<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">物理</a>、工程专业有很强数学背景的学生也欢迎申请。该项目向新生提供有限数量的全额<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，以<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>形式发放。*(7)</li>	<li>统计学（Statistics）开设有MS和PhD学位项目，申请者可在同一申请程序同时申请两个项目。*(8)</li></ul><p>该系设有以下研究领域：</p><ul>	<li>纯数学（Pure Mathematics）</li>	<li>应用数学（Applied Mathematics）</li>	<li>统计学（Statistics）*(4)(10)</li></ul><p><strong>奖学金</strong></p><p>大多数研究生可获得TA奖学金，包括全部学费、9个月生活补助和医疗保险。2015年秋季，PhD新生可得到$18,300生活补助。MS新生通常可获得部分TA，补助金额约$12,900。另有相当数量的PhD可获得教员发放的<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>奖学金。*(9)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>数学和统计学系宣传册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNmhLa4bV7AUHHHHHKUqb6WQZ63OGIJGjmjovgefQXsVjpVkJoT-DH3QVcy6h8NP9QRHpz-zo6FR3Z1NcIA26B_pCmZ1hHvNQ-UfvL4yKdL9NRZmpTSoHv" target="_blank">Mathematics and Statistics at a Glance</a> (PDF)</li>	<li>研究生手册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDOoLzABI-R3pppppp0UQH2SCFk_LuLu9jMnZHF_xdMnZRm_vdguwcQSvsg_WsrU6cMS9jFuuczq" target="_blank">Handbook for Graduate Students</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjonwmHu4dM6pppppJ6pDhm-nIvZTL3d3dy51xNQZ70JMkCYmZUYxV1Xvj8_bZxosgeClS2oEkCBqGik7fKYEO2DtUPd4_We1qdhVBiT-A943QgxiJoBya" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_2hwkcdGHFuOQSL1odmWQBqdy8hgKVdfeCAd4fo2LNZwBmxjUgD4BOxZqPc2mpfs3G6B9SQBmmOPMSCLhbyrDoXESh5jxGfI" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrMpLBGgpDmehdKsNgS4XlKdcinqAycVTlM1wESW_I1yWS-5JQL4nWwUSOD3ZsGStdgX4kux-h_oabFh1tWF70SFoj" target="_blank">CNS Departments</a> College of Natu