a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>和Fellowship形式发放，所有奖学金都包括学费在内。注意MS学位项目没有奖学金。*(6)(8)</p><p>设有以下研究领域：</p><ul>	<li>分子和<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/细胞生物学" target="_blank">细胞生物学</a>（Molecular and Cellular Biology）</li>	<li>基因组学和系统生物学（Genomics and Systems Biology）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/医学" target="_blank">医学</a>微生物学（Medical Microbiology）</li>	<li>环境微生物学（Environmental Microbiology）</li>	<li>生物燃料和生物修复（Bio-Fuels and Bio-Remediation）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>微生物学系宣传册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHC1kTXJRmnn77777lrBCKnDLK7V1ExcmTmedrx8ZW5eoR9OJ_LYsB8rQ3vWELy6PxEydNTNLbD-iwbOr5_SPNFec9U1efcyC6TXA0YK1kq4DnRm6iHVkskvpBqAOw_" target="_blank">Microbiology at a Glance</a> (PDF)</li>	<li>研究生手册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=XrChP9QQkrW5UyhQwwwwwwCpLXhlvPj4p8-H-HsU_oZxgH1HM3cd8c2fqyLHIfg7Ix_b0o7sFi9bW6M8Kp_gRGrQ-NAxKZJk8_jrzD" target="_blank">Graduate Student Handbook</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDOktZGdb-8_LR8D7mDnJVmbPWRMAfOF2kB_p4s7y5Shm376qy_znCWsKHi6HPmS0sZMyVBP4WhPWY9eP569jKr6Q3pzbO5dcsYB9nugEUpYB4EPjbnLU3bMGUR4d" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbykOktZGdU13uuuuuud7QYretszEmTmTxPfo6GlexP1VQZzVmKyVQ2A7Bczo3cyVBfHem2HoLPB5xyTcLS" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oGwLMS38_Jj000Paaaq-NMAbg2K4z6w6wvMRCGUvnvMQnG8FgvqUv06J-0x7I06rIteJ-0EvEteaCcME1GHr9_cWzO6Wdh" target="_blank">Fifth-Year Master&#39;s Program</a>&nbsp;Microbiology College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7gXLCZnSf-7OOOOON8Pfx_DigqVeUeU