k">化学工程</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/机械工程" target="_blank">机械工程</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/生物工程" target="_blank">生物工程</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/生物医学工程" target="_blank">生物医学工程</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/电气工程" target="_blank">电气工程</a>或其相关领域专业学士学位（BA或BS），本科课程包括常规理科课程及微分方程，有化学实验室经历，修读过以下课程中的3门课程：固态物理或<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/凝聚态物理" target="_blank">凝聚态物理</a>、力学或材料、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/材料科学与工程" target="_blank">材料科学与工程</a>、统计热力学、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/分析化学" target="_blank">分析化学</a>，以及高分子科学与工程。成绩优异的学生可获得全额<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>。*(4)(5)(6)</p><p>该系研究生学位项目设有以下研究领域：</p><ul>	<li>Synthetic Polymer <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">Chemistry</a></li>	<li>Soft Materials <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">Physics</a></li>	<li>Nanostructured Materials</li>	<li>Bio-Inspired Materials</li>	<li>Energy and Green Science</li>	<li>High Performance Composites</li>	<li>Electronic Polymers/Devices*(4)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>高分子科学与工程系宣传册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvpkHN_V6zUTTTTTMqkv3HrvuLtg0ZcZr9mDRftAxSm4EftVxNc50fk43Xrg0Ny2y-c2IHtVn1UNDfxMnEX1gRcNn70NGfaOvqwbGIQtcoptwW9r" target="_blank">Polymer Science at a Glance</a> (PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4AscwtkO9fNvI_vBoXPhCTjUwDmjjPyOmDJE8hPs4eAEh1-RGZavxXuG3Ubz36VOp_6zhNX__3mwQS2x13r_yVh8Oeemm0qkuGZCvYLIzF62CwRpuryVFULYTxlB62XX" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9LTDLZv0Op6t_2hbMV-6tbl2L8s-350Ls2ql-mN47kv_TSaoLlToMtaGqLiw7QDrv2YNCwxrwAiFDGAPMqgESyTH2xS1Gv5T3" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://w