uctures</li>	<li>Programming Methodology</li>	<li>Computer Systems Principles</li>	<li>Introduction to Computation</li>	<li>Calculus I, II</li>	<li>Linear Algebra</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/统计学" target="_blank">Statistics</a> I*(4)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>本科课程准备：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YhZLDXYcz1RwbzguYS2po25mfmaTAHPswiV-_XFtIOvwhTF6SS6_wwstiH-JH_rK1pRyb7mqaI7k7pdNacJjauyBv-S-OlIefIh91zgkvtr-n0QvIcis-JU" target="_blank">Undergraduate Preparation</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> College of Natural Sciences UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-GMwr-Keqvu44444ou5ARjDXMlL-_JDJD9OAWnTgRY7UdrjEN_jr5tP2lP9jW5SQom-Wg_iHasgb6pUPQOWgKVm_25veM7TVbqJevrERq71GP24vc_IsK" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2u2L4yTxYJj000000kxdh-gzSYG2nY4Y4fhCMnG8FgvMetUiLrUzfC5C_3QWBrZoZgJ9eR-q1kWaLYbtowKl2bNm" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHCkkniNS4L6FWa6aRCRFM3bF6r_iwScMrYz37VVKBdjjm_7IG2fzYYjYojWvKY_7-g7h4F9Yj6rQKgoPUXrIGysrnYw1K0K1zb3_C8R" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Graduate Admissions Questions</a>&nbsp;School of Computer Science UMass Amherst</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWAskL3ojCW8GGGGGicY6lUiHlTDKOph0hHeZhTe0E4IHhTe-EU4KJMLBE7aHJ7XBdTXZWARBj79ZMPGEpZYx_3oS4D-8BnGEpZoS" target="_blank">Application to the Graduate Program</a>&nbsp;School of Computer Science UMass Amherst</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhfmwnkBwXqHoooooohLySZFyvaVOIMeMF6gMv6e3WuFMv6Oe_UwWgKVm_25Jg2im4FiJZONpivsw5hu7VkCMdDulTDpoTkIoy" target="_blank">Joining our Graduate Program</a> School of Computer Science UMass Amherst</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h