>语音学（phonetics）</li>	<li>语言<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/心理学" target="_blank">心理学</a>（psycholinguistics）</li>	<li>语言习得（language acquisition）</li>	<li>形态学（morphology）</li>	<li>最优化理论（Optimality Theory）</li></ul><p>语言学系许多研究生毕业生成为理论语言学（Theoretical Linguistics）领域的教授，作为TOP4的理论语言学项目，每年接受130余份申请，但仅录取5-8人。*(1)(2)</p><p><strong>奖学金</strong></p><p>所有PhD学生可获得全额奖学金，2013-2014学年奖学金补助金额为$20,307，另外，奖学金还包括全部学费、课程注册费和医疗费，许多学生还可获得暑期补贴。*(2)(5)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZiRLuKMyYDQnnnnnnm1JbA-H9dlPZPZBDWLice-BDFjJYdLyFNjPXx-Pbx6P2djP_MjJXMahmQIunzSMizR6x" target="_blank">Ph.D. in Linguistics</a>&nbsp;Department of Linguistics UMass Amherst</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pWcw1hiqHgRllllletoSnU1vrVJaEaEBmus6Wb1Bm-QS4UCJcKM5URy-6JEfHJKNwmQJ_oah6mVO_z08RdAh6tQx6taZ_zE8RobRZdlDxBYJH1wNxTI4rXlanXwag" target="_blank">How to Apply</a>&nbsp;Department of Linguistics UMass Amherst</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8zJkIT16dJL-----ZLcqNFolJCjvEIEIwkdYpmAu4AIJn2qDnGhjn2Cl8H7DeF7jnHKN4GCNe3Itm3p_eRJt43JDiBdT8Hygb0E7O-E47BdUa" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDyhk5gArqUs8TQtvaPzNVzeg9j_UsOvsSO-3zVAlLt-k_lc07sIwIUmhcBByXgYB1iTfJDBUIzDDBATvmpYMw5Y3uUNjeDaf" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQuH3L8zwPUv8gToCURwPwYQpkV-hcb12Yy-utPpu43rC-aJXMXhbTfS_BzuZ_fT-PFZqEpHgrelEVtxbLqtoqL3U" target="_blank">Financial Aid</a>&nbsp;Department of Linguistics UMass Amherst</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>音乐与舞蹈</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.78%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.32%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.98%">			<p>学费（/学期）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>$17,293.5