anmu.org/阿默斯特学院" target="_blank">阿默斯特学院</a>（Amherst College）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/史密斯学院" target="_blank">史密斯学院</a>（Smith College）*(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHN7HwSnOKc6MHHHHHH4mvLF-1yu25KA8VU9-CGrqlU9HfDF1fGA1C0jp5GAqhZVUdGM-dsMHhZroCGHijZ7fOkGy" target="_blank">Admissions</a> Department of Economics UMass Amherst</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrMWLs_unRKw1-73YXw7Z1Ced52-JAxdBqrbqW9LfSu90aFguoDAui-2AlLg2s7tgUPFJxTL-72TKgnfuwDh53FkAor6yWV1vaE-NbXLCQxf-NFaI8b-0aQg_7mjjG" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_25wfFe8hfrffffffjdwGzQOEteS5S5_VprZlAIzPBqjEN_jr5tjEuWGH4_Zf4tjHbFzruFZ9BI8y598K0" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7mgawJr7tUXRYN52_xFU9jt3rPkfAQch59w-fo1WCFh2SFyOZBjtjsFPk2o-aTLdxHdxR2plODbuS9OlmBTRjO" target="_blank">4+1 Accelerated Master&#39;s Degree</a> Department of Economics UMass Amherst</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6bbw4VCA_ElkkkkkkYu24ViGWO6feS5S5_Vp-Yoa-69OgeO-BdO7Ddy2gByWcVhmamnHI1pXuPYVB" target="_blank">Graduate Program</a> Department of Economics UMass Amherst</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>资源经济学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:76px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:76px">			<p>学费（/学期）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:94px">			<p>$17,293.50</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>2月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:95px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank