学</a>、运动生理学、运动控制、和生物力学，但有些申请者其中一门或多门课程未修读也被录取，这种情况下，前置课程必须在入学后最短的时间内修读完毕。</p><p>运动学研究生项目每年招生人数都有变化，MS可选择性参加<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/面试" target="_blank">面试</a>，PhD强烈建议参加面试。*(3)</p><p>该项目向研究生择优提供<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>，一般包括全部学费、医疗保险、生活补助以及某些其他费用。基本上所有研究生均可获得<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，无需单独申请。另外公共卫生学院向该项目提供有限数量的Fellowship。*(6)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkMogLIup4FpaRRRRRRETYGJphQcu61MFMFnETQI2o69_gP4peyMIvDZ9Fk9AFEjxrAUp9foEtisay_sL6SCXpzUKJ" target="_blank">Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.umass.edu/bursar/tuition/graduate-tuition-rates" target="_blank">Tuition and Fees</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDNkGpktrRa333333MnIfxh0Soc7U7U2mHbEnJImkHOayXgm1SDFy5gFAORqdRVtQhewdjmwnUV9dlTgYUV8yhzmQU582h5wQXa" target="_blank">Admissions</a>&nbsp;Department of Kinesiology UMass Amherst</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8W6LFLdYT_Ztttttt-pZMtTeh6yAUBUBiSj0CzLeiSn4MNyeUf6ZM5yXim-3QHPVFmXjQ9IjKvPpQ4DnivPgcmQp0B" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a>&nbsp;Department of Kinesiology UMass Amherst</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNW5khMQansdNNNNN7dU8AKtb1_ITLTLpnClyXRtpnYe8c_eTsXVUp6MX_vWKpqWdAv8E6nUEpZoSVZiCp3wS6ZwKp1fx6Mu943wTeswL2ur-N" target="_blank">Admissions Requirements</a>&nbsp;UMass Amherst Graduate School</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWS9Iw0DYWVTCAAAAABBBFYZBVdWECvxBxB2XF-Yoa-69Og84nVJhAE-_sklrsd0B7wnH5MisYnldC9onD9tQoeTQokfdbaPMAVxO5tuJ2fphkM7fIUFvh" target="_blank">Department At a Glance</a>&nbsp;Department of Kinesiology UMass Amherst</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrk2wjNSrTEafHgW4gO3f6lSvlWhorazNvBqOmSSa_6m4fsTebUvVA18SOhQieBfoVZVnUi118h06FhMzBAiFz_600F